  <title>Concrete toolkit tabbed component</title>
  <para>
  	A <emphasis>tabbed</emphasis> component is a container that allows you to switch between multiple groups of
  	components within a single area.
  </para>
  <para role="tip">
  	Please keep in mind that it is not possible to object map a single component within the container but only the container as
  	a whole. To switch between the single components you have to use the according actions. 
  </para>
